# Phase 3 — Backend Quota Enforcement Walkthrough

## Changes Made

### 1. User Model — [User.js](file:///c:/Users/dasar/DropGravity%20Pro/server/models/User.js)

Added 4 quota fields **at the end of the schema** (before `module.exports`):

| Field | Type | Default | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| `dailySearchCount` | Number | 0 | Tracks free searches used today |
| `dailyAdUnlockCount` | Number | 0 | Tracks ads watched today (max 2) |
| `bonusSearchCredits` | Number | 0 | Extra searches earned via ads |
| `lastResetDate` | String | null | YYYY-MM-DD in UTC for daily reset |

---

### 2. Quota Utility — [quotaUtils.js](file:///c:/Users/dasar/DropGravity%20Pro/server/utils/quotaUtils.js) `[NEW]`

- [getTodayDateString()](file:///c:/Users/dasar/DropGravity%20Pro/server/utils/quotaUtils.js#8-14) — returns UTC date as `YYYY-MM-DD`
- [resetDailyQuotaIfNeeded(user)](file:///c:/Users/dasar/DropGravity%20Pro/server/utils/quotaUtils.js#15-32) — compares `lastResetDate` to today, resets all daily counters if mismatched, saves to DB

---

### 3. Analyze Route — [index.js](file:///c:/Users/dasar/DropGravity%20Pro/server/index.js#L142-L204)

`POST /api/products/analyze` changes:
- Made handler `async`
- Loads user from DB via `User.findById(req.userId)`
- **User existence check** → 404 if `!user` (per architect correction)
- Calls [resetDailyQuotaIfNeeded(user)](file:///c:/Users/dasar/DropGravity%20Pro/server/utils/quotaUtils.js#15-32)
- **Quota check** (free users): 3 base + bonus credits, returns 403 if exhausted
- **Pro bypass**: no quota checks for `plan === 'pro'`
- **Post-generation deduction**: increments `dailySearchCount` or decrements `bonusSearchCredits`
- Deterministic engine calls (`generateProducts`, `getSignalStrength`) **unchanged**

---

### 4. Ad-Complete Endpoint — [index.js](file:///c:/Users/dasar/DropGravity%20Pro/server/index.js#L253-L293) `[NEW]`

`POST /api/ad-complete` (protected with [verifyToken](file:///c:/Users/dasar/DropGravity%20Pro/server/middleware/verifyToken.js#3-29)):
- User existence check → 404
- Pro users rejected → 400
- Max 2 ads/day → 403 if exceeded
- Awards 2 `bonusSearchCredits` per ad

